            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Albanus Balvi <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>dec</abbr><ex>urio</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>ala</abbr><ex>e</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Augusta</abbr><ex>e</ex></expan> Ituraeo<lb break="no" n="3"/>rum domo Betavos <note>sic</note> an<lb break="no" n="4"/><expan><abbr>nor</abbr><ex>um</ex></expan> XLII stipendiorum <lb n="5"/>XX hic situs est titulum <lb n="6"/>memoriae posuerunt <lb n="7"/><expan><abbr>Tib</abbr><ex>erius</ex></expan> Iulius Reitugenus et <lb n="8"/>Lucanus <expan><abbr>dec</abbr><ex>uriones</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>ala</abbr><ex>e</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>ustae</ex></expan> <lb n="9"/>Ituraeorum
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Oberhalb des Inschriftfeldes zwei Pferde mit Pferdeführer; darüber ehemals eine männliche Büste (nur durch eine Zeichnung überliefert).</p>
            </div>
